---
import * as icon from "lucide-react";
import ContactForm from "./ContactForm";
---

<section
  id="contact"
  class="min-h-screen container mx-auto flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-20"
>
  <div class="h-full flex items-center justify-center gap-10">
    <div
      class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full text-xl space-y-10"
    >
      <h3 class="w-full text-gray-400">CONTACTO</h3>
      <h2
        class="text-2xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold gradient-text-green py-3 w-full"
      >
        Creemos algo extraordinario juntos
      </h2>
      <p>
        Siempre estoy abierto a conversar sobre nuevos proyectos, ideas
        creativas u oportunidades para formar parte de tu visión. Si tienes
        alguna pregunta o simplemente quieres saludar, no dudes en contactarme.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6 w-full">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Correo electrónico</p>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">
            <a
              href="mailto:jesu.o.sandoval@gmail.com"
              class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-lg text-white transition-colors hover:text-emerald-400"
            >
              <icon.Mail className="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-400" />
              <span
                class="border-b border-transparent group-hover:border-emerald-400"
              >
                jesu.o.sandoval@gmail.com
              </span>
            </a>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Redes Sociales</p>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-white flex items-center gap-6">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/jesuSando/"
              class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-lg text-white transition-colors hover:text-emerald-400"
            >
              <icon.GithubIcon className="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-400" />
              <span
                class="border-b border-transparent group-hover:border-emerald-400"
              >
                GitHub
              </span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jesús-sandoval-martínez-983112292"
              class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-lg text-white transition-colors hover:text-emerald-400"
            >
              <icon.Linkedin className="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-400" />
              <span
                class="border-b border-transparent group-hover:border-emerald-400"
              >
                LinkedIn
              </span>
            </a>
          </h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full">
      <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <ContactForm client:load />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
